要睇貴既 出名既<br />\n西醫智障 係唔係都幫你打石膏 等佢自己好返就算"},{"pid":"72c2a4c3f087606a65840d3064b0b772dc8691e1","tid":25030,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"去睇急症，照x光，無骨折骨裂就唔洗理"},{"pid":"60fb404ecfd6730776638d7b88f4b36ca159250e","tid":25030,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇跌打 不過一定要睇貴既 出名既<br />\n西醫智障 係唔係都幫你打石膏 等佢自己好返就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果係入面有事跌打會唔會仲衰？<br />\n我都唔知睇西定跌打好<br />\n未試過手腳有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322e577a9650c469ae5b87bce4d0f37ef06167e1","tid":25030,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去睇急症，照x光，無骨折骨裂就唔洗理</blockquote><br />\n韌帶x光照唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bcee2b3a5b680cd136cc7942883941c908a37d","tid":25030,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇跌打 不過一定要睇貴既 出名既<br />\n西醫智障 係唔係都幫你打石膏 等佢自己好返就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果係入面有事跌打會唔會仲衰？<br />\n我都唔知睇西定跌打好<br />\n未試過手腳有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇西醫斷左證先<br />\n無斷無裂就再睇跌打<br />\n有斷有裂既你都係得石膏一條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dc9a5c5b3bb128c6108d0177ddd49f20c04c12","tid":25030,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇跌打 不過一定要睇貴既 出名既<br />\n西醫智障 係唔係都幫你打石膏 等佢自己好返就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果係入面有事跌打會唔會仲衰？<br />\n我都唔知睇西定跌打好<br />\n未試過手腳有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇西醫斷左證先<br />\n無斷無裂就再睇跌打<br />\n有斷有裂既你都係得石膏一條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過裂骨 全程睇跌打冇打過石膏 依家啲跌打斷唔到證會叫你去照個x光先 再斷證 <br />\n<br />\n但係如果睇跌打，一定要睇貴 同出名既 <br />\n試過去啲平平地既街鋪 差好遠 醫左好耐"},{"pid":"68f0ef8db03b70ad3e8e6a2fcc36f1be761e4cb6","tid":25030,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:59:58.000Z","msg":"痛到行唔到 連落床都好難<br />\n覺得去搭taxi呢段路都好遠好難行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9ac83f82c6629d737da3418ad11c08b73ccd66","tid":25030,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痛到行唔到 連落床都好難<br />\n覺得去搭taxi呢段路都好遠好難行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打既話搵人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打 頂硬上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc2eb86e719d8a3dd5dec3b779b3f85c9082ee4","tid":25030,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"而家 d 人 真係愈嚟愈智障<br />\n<br />\n有事唔撚去睇醫生 上黎開post 問 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母正常少少都唔會咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}